folder: New Lots Avenue & Hendrix Street, Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: New Lots Avenue - Hendrix Street
text:
(1)  507-607 New Lots Ave, North side, between Hendrix Street and Schenck Ave., showing the Van Siclen farmhouse. No. 597 is at the extreme left.
About 1900.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
The same, another view, showing only the Van Siclen house.
About 1900.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
